text: Roland Diethart (born 3 August 1973) is an Austrian cross-country skier. He competed in the men's relay event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Austria Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Leoben
